#: ../../source/tui.md:1
msgid "终端 TUI（Textual）"
msgstr "Terminal TUI (Textual)"

#: ../../source/tui.md:3
msgid "SimpleLLMFunc 提供了开箱即用的 TUI 装饰器，基于 `textual` + `event stream` 构建。"
msgstr ""
"SimpleLLMFunc provides an out-of-the-box TUI decorator built on `textual` + "
"`event stream`."

#: ../../source/tui.md:5
msgid "你可以把它直接叠加在 `@llm_chat` 上，让 Agent 具备完整的终端输入循环、流式渲染和工具调用可视化。"
msgstr ""
"You can stack it directly on `@llm_chat` so your agent gains a full terminal"
" input loop, streaming rendering, and tool-call visualization."

#: ../../source/tui.md:7
msgid ""
"提示：`@tui` 依赖事件流，务必在 `@llm_chat` 中设置 `enable_event=True`，并推荐开启 `stream=True` "
"以获得流式渲染体验。"
msgstr ""
"Tip: `@tui` relies on the event stream, be sure to set `enable_event=True` "
"in `@llm_chat`, and it is recommended to enable `stream=True` for a "
"streaming rendering experience."

#: ../../source/tui.md:9
msgid "安装依赖"
msgstr "Install Dependencies"

#: ../../source/tui.md:11
msgid "`textual` 已作为框架依赖。"
msgstr "`textual` is already included as a framework dependency."

#: ../../source/tui.md:13
msgid "如果你在已有环境中升级，请重新安装依赖："
msgstr ""
"If you upgraded inside an existing environment, reinstall dependencies:"

#: ../../source/tui.md:19
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../source/tui.md:40
msgid "`@tui` 会自动识别输入参数："
msgstr "`@tui` will automatically recognize input parameters"

#: ../../source/tui.md:42
msgid "`history` / `chat_history` 作为历史参数"
msgstr "`history` / `chat_history` as history parameter"

#: ../../source/tui.md:43
msgid "其余第一个参数作为用户输入"
msgstr "The rest of the first parameter is used as user input"

#: ../../source/tui.md:45
msgid "UI 能力"
msgstr "UI Capabilities"

#: ../../source/tui.md:47
msgid "用户消息与模型消息交替渲染"
msgstr "Alternate rendering of user and model messages"

#: ../../source/tui.md:48
msgid "模型流式输出实时刷新，并支持 Markdown 渲染"
msgstr ""
"Model streaming output refreshes in real time and supports Markdown "
"rendering"

#: ../../source/tui.md:49
msgid "流式输出期间消息区自动跟随到底部，优先展示最新内容"
msgstr ""
"During streaming output, the message area auto-scrolls to the bottom to keep"
" the latest content visible."

#: ../../source/tui.md:50
msgid "推理增量（reasoning delta）以灰色文本展示（当模型提供该字段时）"
msgstr "Reasoning deltas are shown in gray text (when provided by the model)"

#: ../../source/tui.md:51
msgid "每次模型调用结束后，在消息下方展示耗时与 token 用量"
msgstr ""
"After each model call completes, display elapsed time and token usage under "
"the message"

#: ../../source/tui.md:52
msgid "工具调用开始时展示结构化参数（可读格式，不是裸 JSON 字符串）"
msgstr ""
"Show structured tool arguments at tool-call start (readable format, not raw "
"JSON strings)"

#: ../../source/tui.md:53
msgid "工具执行期间消费 `CustomEvent` 并实时更新工具输出"
msgstr ""
"Consume `CustomEvent` during tool execution and update tool output in real "
"time"

#: ../../source/tui.md:54
msgid "当工具（如 PyRepl）触发 `input()` 时，输入框自动切换为工具输入模式并优先回填该请求"
msgstr ""
"When a tool (such as PyRepl) triggers `input()`, the input box automatically"
" switches to tool-input mode and prioritizes submitting to that request."

#: ../../source/tui.md:55
msgid "工具结束后展示结果与调用统计（耗时/状态）"
msgstr ""
"Show tool results and call statistics after completion (duration/status)"

#: ../../source/tui.md:56
msgid "fork 任务自动拆分为独立列，基于 `origin.fork_id` 路由到对应分栏"
msgstr ""
"fork tasks are automatically split into independent columns, routed to "
"corresponding sections based on `origin.fork_id`"

#: ../../source/tui.md:57
msgid "聊天消息区支持超出视口滚动，消息项会随内容自适应高度"
msgstr ""
"The chat message area supports viewport overflow scrolling, and each message"
" item automatically grows with its content."

#: ../../source/tui.md:59
msgid "交互与退出"
msgstr "Interaction and Exit"

#: ../../source/tui.md:61
msgid "发送消息：输入后按 Enter"
msgstr "Send message: press Enter after typing"

#: ../../source/tui.md:62
msgid "当存在待处理的工具输入请求时，Enter 会优先把输入提交给该请求"
msgstr ""
"When a pending tool-input request exists, pressing Enter submits input to "
"that request first."

#: ../../source/tui.md:63
msgid "强制发送新一轮聊天：`/chat <message>`（可在有待处理工具输入时绕过优先路由）"
msgstr ""
"Force a new chat turn: `/chat <message>` (bypasses priority routing while a "
"tool input request is pending)."

#: ../../source/tui.md:64
msgid "复制完整转录：`/copy` 或 `Ctrl+Y`"
msgstr "Copy full transcript: `/copy` or `Ctrl+Y`"

#: ../../source/tui.md:65
msgid "退出命令：`/exit`、`/quit`、`/q`"
msgstr "Exit commands: `/exit`, `/quit`, `/q`"

#: ../../source/tui.md:66
msgid "快捷键退出：`Ctrl+Q`（同时保留 `Ctrl+C`）"
msgstr "Hotkey exit: `Ctrl+Q` (while keeping `Ctrl+C`)"

#: ../../source/tui.md:68
msgid "自定义 Tool 事件 Hook"
msgstr "Custom Tool Event Hook"

#: ../../source/tui.md:70
msgid "`@tui` 支持通过 `custom_event_hook` 注入自定义事件解析逻辑："
msgstr ""
"`@tui` supports injecting custom event parsing logic via "
"`custom_event_hook`:"

#: ../../source/tui.md:95
msgid ""
"框架也内置了部分常见工具事件的默认解析（例如 PyRepl 的 "
"`kernel_stdout`/`kernel_stderr`/`kernel_input_request`）。"
msgstr ""
"The framework also includes default parsers for common tool events (e.g., "
"PyRepl `kernel_stdout`/`kernel_stderr`/`kernel_input_request`)."

#: ../../source/tui.md:97
msgid "运行示例"
msgstr "Run the Example"

#: ../../source/tui.md:99
msgid "参考示例：`examples/tui_chat_example.py`"
msgstr "Example: `examples/tui_chat_example.py`"
